title: Live Downtown with Covered Parking included!
map_address: 111 Kellogg Blvd E near Robert St
posting_body: ['Apartment 1210 (Fountain)', '1Bedroom - 750 sq/ft', 'Rent $1425', 'Lease terms 12 months', 'Parking included/1 spot in covered garage', 'Application Fee: $35 per adult', 'Security Deposit: $400', 'Administrative fee: $150', 'Pet Deposit: $200, Pet Non-Refundable Deposit: $100-200 per pet', 'Cat Rent: $15/month, Dog Rent: $40/month', 'Apply by August 15 and receive a $300 Visa gift card.', 'Come and be a part of an amazing community!', 'Downtown St. Paul has so much to culture to offer from the beautiful theaters, museums, farmers markets, concert and sports.', 'And downtown also offers you your new home at Kellogg Square!', 'Apartment 1210 features large windows spanning the living room and bedroom allowing you tons of natural light.', ' At Kellogg Square you will find many amazing amenities including indoor pool and hot tub, 24 hour fitness center, and for your four legged friends a pet spa!', 'Flip through the attached pictures to see additional amenities.', 'Kellogg Square is proudly owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a tour today!', 'Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
